39:17.916 --> 39:20.685
Mom? What's the matter?

39:22.788 --> 39:25.823
Nothing. It's...

39:26.191 --> 39:29.293
just... you, that's all.

39:31.697 --> 39:33.831
Evie?

39:36.969 --> 39:39.637
I love you.
