40:05.030 --> 40:07.031
For all of us?

40:09.401 --> 40:10.835
I love the purple.

40:14.106 --> 40:16.107
Yeah, me too.

41:01.253 --> 41:03.254
How you holding up?

41:05.891 --> 41:07.892
