41:09.795 --> 41:11.763
I'm sorry.

41:12.598 --> 41:15.199
I can't imagine the pain
you're going through.

41:17.236 --> 41:20.138
But I want you to know,
whatever you need, I'm here.

41:22.007 --> 41:25.076
I've always been here for
you, Jimmy. You know that.

41:28.847 --> 41:30.414
Is Alec a suspect?

41:30.449 --> 41:34.018
No. He's no longer a POI and
they're no longer looking for him.

41:36.088 --> 41:38.489
- Thank you.
- Don't thank me.

41:42.694 --> 41:44.195
Alec didn't do it, Jimmy.

41:47.299 --> 41:49.267
Who you looking for?

41:49.301 --> 41:51.335
There's a warrant out.

41:53.572 --> 41:55.706
For Grace Travis.

41:59.344 --> 42:02.246
They found her fingerprints
on a gun on the pier.

42:11.857 --> 42:14.025
You told me
you took care of her.

42:16.128 --> 42:18.129
You told me you got rid of her.

42:30.342 --> 42:32.677
I think I'm ready to start
baby-sitting professionally.

42:32.711 --> 42:34.245
I'm old enough.
Miranda does it.

42:34.279 --> 42:36.280
Oh, if Miranda does it...

42:36.315 --> 42:39.584
Oh, my God, she was giving
Cooper Abaire his bath,

42:39.618 --> 42:41.619
