42:41.653 --> 42:43.688
Evie!

42:45.057 --> 42:47.592
Did you know two-year-olds
could get boners?

42:48.594 --> 42:50.895
So where have you two been?
Whose car is this?

42:50.929 --> 42:53.464
I'm not even gonna tell you
what she just said.

42:53.498 --> 42:56.167
Really? Could somebody
tell me what's going on?

42:56.201 --> 42:58.236
- Er... no.
- Ta-dah!

42:59.771 --> 43:01.639
Look at you.

43:01.673 --> 43:05.109
You're so pretty.
