43:41.580 --> 43:44.382
I fucked up, Tommy.
I fucked everything...

43:44.416 --> 43:47.518
- I fucked everything up.
- What are you talking about?

43:50.956 --> 43:54.759
I'm so sorry.
I didn't mean to hurt you.

43:57.829 --> 44:00.531
- Mom, please don't...
- Please, please forgive me.

44:03.669 --> 44:05.102
Do you have to do this here?

44:05.137 --> 44:07.772
I'm sorry. You know
I'm gonna have to cuff you.

44:09.241 --> 44:12.576
Grace Travis, you are under arrest on
suspicion of the murder of Max Laszlo.

44:12.611 --> 44:14.845
- Mom?
- Grace?

44:14.880 --> 44:18.215
- and will be used against you in a court
of law. - Your daddy loves you very much.

44:18.250 --> 44:20.117
- Mom...
- Your mom's gonna be okay.

44:20.152 --> 44:22.620
